trans-unit.target: TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MEESIYA_000_050<tab>At last... The power to reclaim what is mine. What is <var 1A 02 /var>ours<var 1A 01 /var>...
TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MEESIYA_000_051<tab>The will of Queen Gunnhildr shall not be denied. All who oppose Bozja must fall.
TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MIKOTO_000_052<tab>By the gods... She has become a vessel for the blade's power!
TEXT_DUNGEONMYC2_00000_MEESIYA_000_100<tab>No... No, we have suffered too long for it to end this way. Bozja is <var 1A 02 /var>ours<var 1A 01 /var>! If we cannot have it, no one will!
